ğŸ–¥ï¸ What is it?
EC2 is a virtual server in AWS where you can run applications, host websites, or deploy services.

ğŸ” Key Features:
Choose instance types (CPU, memory, GPU, etc.)

Connect via SSH
Install any OS (Linux, Windows, etc.)
